<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Tamagochi_Start</title>
    <style>
      .title {
        text-align: center;
        font-family: Phosphate;
        font-size: 48px;
        margin-top: 0px;
        padding-top: 0px;
        margin-bottom: 0px;
        padding-bottom: 0px;
      }
      
      .title-description {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 0px;
        padding-top: 0px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        padding-bottom: 0px;
        font-family: Phosphate;
        font-size: 30px;
      }
      
      form {
        position: fixed;
 		left: 50%;
 		margin-left: -173px;
 		font-family: Phosphate;
 		font-size: 20px;
      }
      
      input {
        font-size: 20px;
      }
      
      .button {
        position: fixed;
 		left: 50%;
 		margin-top: 10px;
 		text-decoration: none;
        display: inline-block;
  		padding: 12px 40px;
  		margin: 10px 20px;
  		margin-left: -65px;
 	 	border-radius: 30px;
  		background-image: linear-gradient(45deg, #6ab1d7 0%, #33d9de 50%, #002878 100%);
  		background-position: 100% 0;
  		background-size: 200% 200%;
  		font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
  		font-size: 18px;
  		font-weight: 300;
  		color: white;
  		box-shadow: 0 16px 32px 0 rgba(0, 40, 120, .35);
  		transition: .5s;
      }
	  .button:hover {
  		box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(0, 40, 120, 0);
  		background-position: 0 0;
	  }
	  
	  html {
	    background-image: url(https://images.pexels.com/photos/325185/pexels-photo-325185.jpeg);
		background-repeat: no-repeat;
		background-position: center center;
		background-attachment: fixed;
		-webkit-background-size: cover;
		-moz-background-size: cover;
		-o-background-size: cover;
		background-size: cover;
	  }
	  
	  .firstname {
	    margin-bottom: 5px;
	  }
    </style>
  </head>
  
  <body>
    <h1 class="title">Привіт! Вітаю у грі, про твого улюбленця!</h1>
    <p class="title-description">Для початку введи тип та ім'я улюбленця:</p>
    <form action="/set_cookies" method="get">
      <div class="firstname">
      Тип улюбленця:&nbsp; 
      <input type='text' name='type' required placeholder="Тип"><br>
      </div>
      Імʼя улюбленця: 
      <input type='text' name='name' required  placeholder="Імʼя"><br>
      <input class="button" type='submit' value='Підтвердити'>
    </form>

  </body>
</html>